Banco Macro Sees 40% Credit Expansion in 2011, Reuters Reports

-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 
2011-03-30T16:24:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-30/banco-macro-sees-40-credit-expansion-in-2011-reuters-reports.html
Argentine lender  Banco Macro SA (BMA) 
expects 40 percent growth in its loan portfolio in 2011, Reuters
said.  The bank is also looking to expand operations in the
trading block that includes Argentina,  Brazil , Uruguay and
Paraguay, Reuters reported, citing a presentation by Banco Macro
Chairman Jorge Brito.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduardo Thomson in Santiago at 
 ethomson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
